<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hearted" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hearted,</orth> seated in the heart: <cit><quote>I hate the Moor; my cause is h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.373" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 373</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thy crown and h. throne,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.448" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 448</bibl></cit>. -- In <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 178</bibl> it makes part of the compound <emph>treble-hearted.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>